test run stages
- populate database once
- run every test within a transaction
- reference (and maybe modify) existing records during test setup/before stage

Machinist blueprints need to be reloaded when models reload





Start the test server with init script:
vendor/adva/spec/test_server/bin/server -l vendor/adva/engines/adva_cms/test_/test_init/test_server/init.rb
vendor/adva/spec/test_server/bin/test vendor/adva/engines/adva_cms/test_/functional/admin/install_controller_test.rb -l 34

